    {
      "id": "3e24adf7_39b37c1d",
      "file_path": "sources/hv-collector-configuration/src/main/kotlin/org/onap/dcae/collectors/veshv/config/impl/HvVesCbsClient.kt",
      "patchset_number": 15,
      "line": 44,
      "message": "Just to polish this function:\n1. there is typo in first log at the end\n2. we can extract `CbsRequests.getConf...` to method and inline variable\n3. in mapping and flatMapping we can use references\n\nSo final would look like:\n```\n    fun configurationUpdates(mdc: MappedDiagnosticContext) = cbsClientMono\n            .doOnNext {\n                logger.info(mdc) {\n                    \"CBS client successfully created, first request will be sent in ${firstRequestDelay.seconds} s\"\n                }\n            }\n            .onErrorLog(logger, mdc) { \"Failed to retrieve CBS client\" }\n            .retryWhen(retry(mdc))\n            .delayElement(firstRequestDelay)\n            .flatMapMany { cbsClient ->\n                Mono.just(configurationRequest())\n                        .repeat()\n                        .map(CbsRequest::withNewInvocationId)\n                        .flatMap(cbsClient::get)\n                        .concatMap {\n                            Mono.just(it).delayElement(requestInterval.get())\n                        }\n                        .distinctUntilChanged()\n            }\n\n    private fun configurationRequest() = CbsRequests.getConfiguration(RequestDiagnosticContext.create())\n```",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3701,
        "name": "Filip Krzywka",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "filip.krzywka@nokia.com",
        "username": "fkrzywka"
      },
      "updated": "2019-06-05 06:08:40.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
